{
  "info": {
    "name": "WealthPro — End-to-End Simulation",
    "_postman_id": "wp-sim-2026-04-19",
    "description": "Full walkthrough of the WealthPro API: admin login, self-registration, staff creation, role-based access, row-level ownership, negative (403) cases.\n\nUsage:\n1. Start the stack: Eureka -> Gateway -> all domain services.\n2. Seed the databases (see SEED section).\n3. Run this collection top-to-bottom. Tokens are captured into variables automatically via test scripts.\n\nDefault credentials (after seeding):\n- admin / Admin@2024\n- client1..client10 / Wealth@2024\n- Staff (rm1, advisor1, dealer1, compliance1) are created via Act 2 with password Rm@2024 etc.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:9999" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "clientToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "clientId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "rmToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "advisorToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "dealerToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "complianceToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "newClientUsername", "value": "testclient01" },
    { "key": "newClientPassword", "value": "Test@2024" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Act 1 — ADMIN login",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/login (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', j.token);",
                  "console.log('Admin token stored. Roles=', j.roles);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@2024\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
